戏去维系感情，23 年 4 月中旬分手了。</p>\n<p>22 年 12 月配置了台式，配置还可以，加上外设之类的约 1.1w 。配台式之前都是一起打手游，目前出现的状况就是我分手了突然很不想打游戏....因为本人之前也是爱好众多：跑步、钻研一些代码、跳舞、读书等等。可能因为恋爱有点过于倾向游戏这一类。</p>\n<p>23 年上半年都在玩 PUBG ，现在游戏搭子的号也被封了，一个人玩也没意思。LOL 还在原来前任那个区，想玩又不想勾起回忆其实可以转区....</p>\n<p>不想浪费自己的电竞桌、电竞椅、光污染主机，以及各种炫酷外设，但是游戏兴趣也不是很大（可能是没有好玩的游戏刺激我，也没有游戏搭子）。</p>\n<p>从事的是嵌入式方面，加班不是很严重，周三周五可以多玩一会儿，周末时间自由那种。</p>\n<p>就很想听听各位 V 友的建议：1.游戏推荐 2.找游戏搭子</p>\n", "last_modified": 1685691750, "replies": 156, "id": 945257}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 4408, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1134, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 615227, "username": "kuingsmile", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kuingsmile", "website": "https://www.horosama.com", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "Kuingsmile", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_mini.png?m=1684770550", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_normal.png?m=1684770550", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_large.png?m=1684770550", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_xlarge.png?m=1684770550", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_xlarge.png?m=1684770550", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/eb03/8672/615227_xlarge.png?m=1684770550", "created": 1676945568, "last_modified": 1684770550}, "last_reply_by": "misaka19000", "last_touched": 1685764705, "title": "查出了不能生育，心里郁闷", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/945348", "created": 1685712238, "deleted": 0, "content": "结婚一年多，查出了 Y 染色体 azfb 缺失，基本不可能有孩子了。老婆很贴心表示以后就过